{"type": "article", "id": 14547, "title": "Miss Mixx落地灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-07T07:00:51Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 20, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606153837Ly15OgPSbjQKcqaY.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这盏简单的灯来自西班牙的设计事务所 The Nude Design。原本是设计师偷懒不想多装饰，因而也成全了简单素雅的造型。白色的灯罩使用了聚丙烯，模拟了一朵花，支架用的胶合板，可以弯折，另外可以单独购买灯吊起来使用。放在客厅或卧室的角落不会抢眼，但有温馨的装点作用。售价 170 欧。<a href=\"http://www.crowdyhouse.com/shop/miss-mixx-floor-lamp/\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142035vC6ybFp8Z53qxMU9.jpg\" width=\"940\" height=\"652\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.69361702\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142036Y2cighVqxUF7ALBN.jpg\" width=\"460\" height=\"460\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016072614203679NhfHKr2a40JjMZ.jpg\" width=\"460\" height=\"460\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}